{"root":{"data":{"id":"cbx15uqmh1s0","created":1623032947362,"text":"生活没有方向、迷茫怎么办"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"cbx16p6wvd40","created":1623033013650,"text":"迷茫的定义","layout_mind_offset":{"x":-42,"y":-196}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"cbx172xz7io0","created":1623033043585,"text":"不知道自己下一步要做什么，找不到生活的愿景和期望"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"cbx17q4ygyo0","created":1623033094073,"text":"事实上，没有人不迷茫"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"cbx187pqdgg0","created":1623033132334,"text":"如何解决","layout_mind_offset":{"x":32,"y":210}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"cbx18dpio140","created":1623033145382,"text":"1.弄清楚你迷茫的源头是什么？没有钱，被某件事困扰还是什么","layout_right_offset":{"x":17,"y":-66}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"cbx1gn00jkw0","created":1623033792521,"text":"2弄清楚自己想要什么样的人，努力的方向，设定长远目标","layout_right_offset":{"x":21,"y":-46}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"cbx2fh5pln40","created":1623036522550,"text":"你是谁，你想成为什么样的人？你喜欢什么事情？你适合什么样的工作？你的未来要追求什么？"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"cbx198vfrbk0","created":1623033213220,"text":"4.听名人的演讲，直观感受大佬的思维和眼界，是走出迷茫最快的方式","layout_right_offset":{"x":16,"y":201}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"cbx1s7vdrog0","created":1623034699959,"text":"3.如果一时半会找不到努力/喜欢的方向","layout_right_offset":{"x":27,"y":-49}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"cbx1soi2yo00","created":1623034736160,"text":"1.尽全力解决一个自己的缺点，把短板补齐","layout_right_offset":{"x":-8,"y":-52}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"cbx1t2j76u00","created":1623034766703,"text":"2.“干掉”一个同学/同事","layout_right_offset":{"x":-3,"y":-20}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"cbx1tepa6pk0","created":1623034793192,"text":"3.整理一切旧东西(旧思维，旧知识)"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"cbx1bkenyk80","created":1623033395056,"text":"迷茫的原因","layout_mind_offset":{"x":567,"y":3}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"cbx1bukm49k0","created":1623033417183,"text":"1没有清晰的自我认知，所以不清楚未来的目标","layout_right_offset":{"x":501,"y":-73}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"cbx1cba9nxs0","created":1623033453563,"text":"不妨试着问一下自己，你是谁，你想成为什么样的人？你喜欢什么事情？你适合什么样的工作？你的未来要追求什么？","layout_right_offset":{"x":1046,"y":2}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"cbx1dbkqp080","created":1623033532560,"text":"2.面临的选择太多，不知道该怎么选才是对的，无法确定哪一个选择才是最优解","layout_right_offset":{"x":663,"y":20}},"children":[]}]}]},"template":"default","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}